data.description:
So much to offer! Welcome home to this charming 3 bed, 2 bath single-family gem on a generous 1/3 acre lot. Tiled throughout, this move-in-ready residence boasts a spacious 2-car garage with plenty of cabinets to keep you organized. You'll appreciate the metal roof and new hurricane-rated garage door for added durability, along with security cameras for peace of mind. Includes a new washing machine, 1-year new range and central vac! Stay cool year-round with the recently installed 2-year-old, 4-ton A/C system. The property is equipped with a sprinkler system fed by a brand-new well. Your outdoor oasis awaits with a refreshing pool, perfect for relaxation and entertaining, featuring a newer commercial-grade pump. Bring your toys! There's plenty of room to store a boat or RV on the sides of the house, and a shed is included.
Enjoy the tranquility of a well-kept and quiet neighborhood, complemented by an active neighborhood watch for added security. Beyond the peaceful surroundings, you'll find yourself conveniently located near grocery stores, restaurants, and shopping destinations. Don't miss the opportunity to make this meticulously maintained and move-in-ready residence your new home sweet home!
